                                                 m_application.Project.DriverSpecialties.Remove(D);                                                  break;                                              }                                          }                                          m_application.Project.DriverSpecialties.Add(ds);                                          resultOrder.DriverSpecialties.Add(ds);                                      }                                  }                                  break;                                case "X":                                  string x = row["X"].ToString();                                  if (x != "" && x != null)                                      if (Double.TryParse(row["X"].ToString()' out tempX))                                      {                                          if (tempX >= -180.0 && tempX <= 180.0 && tempX != 0.0)                                          {                                              geocodeProvided = true;                                              geocodeCorrect = true;                                          }                                          else if (tempX == 0.0)                                              geocodeCorrect = true;                                      }                                    break;                                case "Y":                                  string y = row["Y"].ToString();                                  if (y != "" && y != null)                                      if (Double.TryParse(row["Y"].ToString()' out tempY))                                      {                                          if (tempY >= -90.0 && tempY <= 90.0 && tempY != 0)                                          {                                              geocodeProvided = true;                                              geocodeCorrect = true;                                          }                                          else if (tempY == 0.0)                                              geocodeCorrect = true;                                      }                                    break;                              #endregion                          }
